{"title_page": "Arne Larsson (footballer)", "text_new": "{{Infobox football biography\n|embed          = \n|name           = Arne Larsson\n|image          = \n|image_size     = \n|alt            = \n|caption        = \n|fullname       = \n|birth_date     = {{birth date and age|1931|04|27|df=yes}}\n|birth_place    = \n|death_date     = \n|death_place    = \n|height         = \n|position       = [[Defender (association football)|Defender]]\n|youthyears1    = \n|youthclubs1    = \n|years1         = \n|clubs1         = [[Djurg\u00e5rdens IF Fotboll|Djurg\u00e5rden]]\n|caps1          = \n|goals1         = \n|totalcaps      = \n|totalgoals     = \n|nationalyears1 = 1954\n|nationalteam1  = [[Sweden national football team|Sweden]] \n|nationalcaps1  = 3\n|nationalgoals1 = 0\n|medaltemplates = \n}}\n'''Arne Larsson''' (born 27 April 1931) is a Swedish former [[association football|footballer]] who played as a [[defender (association football)|defender]]. He made three appearances for [[Sweden national football team|Sweden]].<ref>{{NFT|41737}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Larsson, Arne}}\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:1931 births]]\n[[Category:Association football defenders]]\n[[Category:Swedish footballers]]\n[[Category:Sweden international footballers]]\n[[Category:Allsvenskan players]]\n[[Category:Djurg\u00e5rdens IF Fotboll players]]\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox football biography\n|embed          = \n|name           = Arne Larsson\n|image          = \n|image_size     = \n|alt            = \n|caption        = \n|fullname       = \n|birth_date     = {{birth date and age|1931|04|27|df=yes}}\n|birth_place    = \n|death_date     = \n|death_place    = \n|height         = \n|position       = \n|youthyears1    = \n|youthclubs1    = \n|collegeyears1  = \n|college1       = \n|collegecaps1   = \n|collegegoals1  = \n|years1         = \n|clubs1         = [[Djurg\u00e5rdens IF Fotboll|Djurg\u00e5rden]]\n|caps1          = \n|goals1         = \n|totalcaps 